{0 FAlCon: Algorithmic Control Units}

OCaml-native framework for high-performance signal analysis and control.

{1 Core Modules}

- {!Falcon.Base_acu}: Core lifecycle and state management.
- {!Falcon.Signal_analyzer_base}: Foundation for signal processing logic.
- {!Falcon.Acu_templates}: Pre-built ACU patterns (Simple, Optimizer, Autotuner).
- {!Falcon.Acu_api}: Unified API for unit interaction.
- {!Falcon.Ui_api}: API for UI/Dashboard integration.

{1 Architecture & Usage}

- {{!page-architecture} Fundamentals}: Hub-and-spoke polyglot model.
- {{!page-developer_guide} Usage}: Quickstart for building and deploying ACUs.

